| int           | string     | decimal32 | decimal64 | date       | timestamp           |
+---------------+------------+-----------+-----------+------------+---------------------+
|          NULL | parquet000 |      NULL |         0 | NULL       | 2024-05-28 17:12:45 |
|          NULL | parquet002 |     0.002 |     20000 | 2024-05-16 | 2024-05-28 19:12:45 |
|          NULL | parquet004 |     0.004 |      NULL | 2024-05-18 | NULL                |
|          NULL | parquet006 |      NULL |     60000 | NULL       | 2024-05-28 23:12:45 |
|          NULL | parquet008 |     0.008 |     80000 | 2024-05-22 | 2024-05-29 01:12:45 |
| 1000000000000 | NULL       |     0.001 |      NULL | 2024-05-15 | NULL                |
| 3000000000000 | NULL       |      NULL |     30000 | 2024-05-17 | 2024-05-28 20:12:45 |
| 5000000000000 | NULL       |     0.005 |     50000 | 2024-05-19 | 2024-05-28 22:12:45 |
| 7000000000000 | NULL       |     0.007 |      NULL | 2024-05-21 | NULL                |
| 9000000000000 | NULL       |      NULL |     90000 | 2024-05-23 | 2024-05-29 02:12:45 |
+---------------+------------+-----------+-----------+------------+---------------------+
